SELECT 
	SRC_fact_mail_delivery.MAIL_DELIVERY_KEY AS MAIL_DELIVERY_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.PROSPECT_KEY AS PROSPECT_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.PROGRAM_KEY AS PROGRAM_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.PROGRAM_INVITATION_ID AS PROGRAM_INVITATION_ID
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.EVENT_RESERVATION_KEY AS EVENT_RESERVATION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY AS SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.ENROLLMENT_ID AS ENROLLMENT_ID
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.TEST_ID AS TEST_ID
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.ENTITY_KEY AS ENTITY_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.ORDER_ID AS ORDER_ID
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.PSC_APPOINTMENT_ID AS PSC_APPOINTMENT_ID
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.MAIL_TEMPLATE_KEY AS MAIL_TEMPLATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.REFERENCEABLE_TYPE AS REFERENCEABLE_TYPE
	,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.MAIL_DELIVERY_ID AS MAIL_DELIVERY_ID

,SRC_dim_program.program_id as program_id
,SRC_dim_user.user_id as person_id
,concat(trim(SRC_dim_program.program_id),'|',trim(ifnull(SRC_fact_mail_delivery.referenceable_type,'Not Provided')) )  as campaign_id
,concat(trim(SRC_dim_program.program_id),'-',trim(ifnull(SRC_fact_mail_delivery.referenceable_type,'Not Provided')) )   as campaign_name
,'NOT PROVIDED' as `status`
,NULL as disposition
,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.created_at_time_key as date_of_contact_time
,SRC_fact_mail_delivery.created_at_date_key  as date_of_contact
,NULL as direction
,NULL as answered_by
,SRC_dim_mail_template.category_name as template

	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_MAIL_DELIVERY SRC_fact_mail_delivery 
left join dim_mail_template SRC_dim_mail_template on SRC_fact_mail_delivery.mail_template_key=SRC_dim_mail_template.mail_template_key
left join dim_program SRC_dim_program on SRC_fact_mail_delivery.program_key=SRC_dim_program.program_key
left join dim_user SRC_dim_user on SRC_fact_mail_delivery.user_key=SRC_dim_user.user_key
	inner join dim_user SRC_dim_user2 on SRC_dim_user2.user_id=SRC_dim_user.user_id and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_current,1)=1 and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_deleted,false)=false
where
SRC_fact_mail_delivery.prospect_key<>1

SELECT 
	SRC_fact_export_items.EXPORT_ITEM_KEY AS EXPORT_ITEM_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.EXPORT_ITEM_ID AS EXPORT_ITEM_ID
	,SRC_fact_export_items.TEST_ID AS TEST_ID
	,SRC_fact_export_items.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.PHYSICIAN_KEY AS PHYSICIAN_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.EXPORT_ITEM_DETAIL_KEY AS EXPORT_ITEM_DETAIL_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.PROGRAM_KEY AS PROGRAM_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.ENTITY_KEY AS ENTITY_KEY
	,SRC_fact_export_items.DELETED_AT AS DELETED_AT

,SRC_dim_program.program_id as program_id
,SRC_dim_user.user_id as person_id
,concat( trim(SRC_dim_program.program_id),'|',trim(SRC_dim_export_item_detail.kind) ) as campaign_id
,concat( trim(SRC_dim_program.program_id),'-',trim(SRC_dim_export_item_detail.kind) )as campaign_name
,'NOT PROVIDED' as `status`
,NULL as disposition
,'000' as date_of_contact_time
,SRC_fact_export_items.created_at_date_key  as date_of_contact
,NULL as direction
,NULL as answered_by
,SRC_dim_export_item_detail.kind as template

	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_EXPORT_ITEMS SRC_fact_export_items 
join dim_export_item_detail SRC_dim_export_item_detail on SRC_fact_export_items.export_item_detail_key=SRC_dim_export_item_detail.export_item_detail_key
left join dim_program SRC_dim_program on SRC_fact_export_items.program_key=SRC_dim_program.program_key
left join dim_user SRC_dim_user on SRC_fact_export_items.user_key=SRC_dim_user.user_key
	inner join dim_user SRC_dim_user2 on SRC_dim_user2.user_id=SRC_dim_user.user_id and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_current,1)=1 and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_deleted,false)=false
where 
SRC_dim_export_item_detail.receiver_type='User' AND SRC_dim_export_item_detail.kind is not null
and SRC_dim_user.user_id=256591

	,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.TEST_TYPE_NAME AS TEST_TYPE_NAME

	,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.TEST_LOCATOR AS TEST_LOCATOR

	,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.APPLICATION_FILE_ID AS APPLICATION_FILE_ID
	,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.FILE_NAME AS FILE_NAME

-- ,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.program_id as program_id
,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.user_id as person_id
,concat( trim(SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.program_id),'|',trim(SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.template_id) ) as campaign_id
,concat( trim(SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.program_id),'-',trim(SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.template_type) ) as campaign_name
,'NOT PROVIDED' as `status`
,NULL as disposition
,'000' as date_of_contact_time
,SRC_dim_fulfillment_items.mailed_date  as date_of_contact
,NULL as direction
,NULL as answered_by
,SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.template_type as template

	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_BIOIQ_ODS_STAGING_DIM_FULFILLMENT_ITEM_TEMPLATES SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates 
left join dim_fulfillment_items SRC_dim_fulfillment_items on SRC_dim_fulfillment_items.fulfillment_items_id=SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.fulfillment_item_id
where 
SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.template_type not in ('TRF','DRE_VOUCHER') AND SRC_dim_fulfillment_item_templates.template_type is not null

SELECT 
	SRC_fact_ivr_call.IVR_CALL_KEY AS IVR_CALL_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.IVR_CALL_ID AS IVR_CALL_ID
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.IVR_APPLICATION_KEY AS IVR_APPLICATION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.ENTITY_KEY AS ENTITY_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.IVR_CALL_DETAIL_KEY AS IVR_CALL_DETAIL_KEY
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.TEST_ID AS TEST_ID
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.DURATION AS DURATION
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.IS_MOST_RECENT AS IS_MOST_RECENT
	,SRC_fact_ivr_call.PROGRAM_KEY AS PROGRAM_KEY

,SRC_dim_program.program_id as program_id
,SRC_dim_user.user_id as person_id
,SRC_dim_ivr_application.ivr_application_id as campaign_id 
,SRC_dim_ivr_application.ivr_application_name as campaign_name
,concat(SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.status,'|',SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.answered_by) as `status`
,SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.disposition as disposition
,SRC_fact_ivr_call.created_at_time_key as date_of_contact_time
,SRC_fact_ivr_call.created_at_date_key as date_of_contact
,SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.direction as direction
,SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.answered_by as answered_by
,SRC_dim_ivr_application.purpose as template

	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_IVR_CALL SRC_fact_ivr_call 
left join fact_ivr_call_policy SRC_fact_ivr_call_policy on SRC_fact_ivr_call.user_key=SRC_fact_ivr_call_policy.user_key and SRC_fact_ivr_call.program_key=SRC_fact_ivr_call_policy.program_key
left join dim_ivr_application SRC_dim_ivr_application on SRC_fact_ivr_call.ivr_application_key=SRC_dim_ivr_application.ivr_application_key
left join dim_ivr_call_detail SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail on SRC_fact_ivr_call.ivr_call_detail_key=SRC_dim_ivr_call_detail.ivr_call_detail_key
left join dim_program SRC_dim_program on SRC_fact_ivr_call.program_key=SRC_dim_program.program_key
left join dim_user SRC_dim_user on SRC_fact_ivr_call.user_key=SRC_dim_user.user_key
	inner join dim_user SRC_dim_user2 on SRC_dim_user2.user_id=SRC_dim_user.user_id and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_current,1)=1 and ifnull(SRC_dim_user2.is_deleted,false)=false
where SRC_fact_ivr_call.user_key>1 
and SRC_fact_ivr_call.test_id is not null

attributes.attrExprVal:
ROW_NUMBER() OVER
(
PARTITION BY
	GetKeys.V_PERSON_KEY , GetKeys.V_COMMUNICATION_CAMPAIGN_KEY ,GetKeys.V_DATE_KEY ,GetKeys.V_TIME_KEY 
ORDER BY
       GetKeys.V_PERSON_KEY , GetKeys.V_COMMUNICATION_CAMPAIGN_KEY ,GetKeys.V_DATE_KEY ,GetKeys.V_TIME_KEY 
)
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY    IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE  SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY   END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_communication_campaign.COMMUNICATION_CAMPAIGN_KEY   IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE  SRC_dim_communication_campaign.COMMUNICATION_CAMPAIGN_KEY   END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_communication_type.COMMUNICATION_TYPE_KEY    IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE SRC_dim_communication_type.COMMUNICATION_TYPE_KEY    END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_communication_purpose.COMMUNICATION_PURPOSE_KEY    IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE SRC_dim_communication_purpose.COMMUNICATION_PURPOSE_KEY    END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_communication_status.COMMUNICATION_STATUS_KEY   IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE  SRC_dim_communication_status.COMMUNICATION_STATUS_KEY   END
CASE WHEN  SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY     IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE   SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY   END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_date.DATE_KEY   IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE  SRC_dim_date.DATE_KEY   END
CASE WHEN SRC_dim_time.TIME_KEY    IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE SRC_dim_time.TIME_KEY    END

sqlParams.paramVal: SELECT	'look_back_days', look_back_days FROM control_look_back_days WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS'

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,

SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_ivr_call.SourceCount   , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_ivr_call.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_ivr_call.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.SRC_fact_ivr_call.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_communications.SourceCount   , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_communications.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_communications.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_communications.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_communications_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'
